        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Q7T2" id="it-역량��분류-체계-개요">IT 역량분류 체계 개요<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/mng/it-%EC%A7%81%EB%AC%B4%EC%A0%9C-sw-%EA%B8%B0%EC%88%A0%EC%9E%90-%EB%93%B1%EA%B8%89%EC%A0%9C/#it-%EC%97%AD%EB%9F%89%EB%B6%84%EB%A5%98-%EC%B2%B4%EA%B3%84-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2>
